OL,3,CExeter Chiefs could soon be under new
OL,4,CAmerican ownership
OL,6,FExeter Chiefs could soon be under new
OL,7,Fownership with plans to give control
OL,8,Fto an American consortium being given
OL,9,Fthe green light by members who
OL,10,Fcurrently own the club.
OL,12,FExeter Chiefs is the only club in the
OL,13,FPrem owned by around 700 members,
OL,14,Fhowever the club needs new investment
OL,15,Fto continue to challenge for honours
OL,16,Fat the top level.
