OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1778328667
OL,3,CExeter Chiefs could soon be under new
OL,4,CAmerican ownership
OL,6,FMembers and shareholders of Exeter
OL,7,FRugby Club Group plc gathered at the
OL,8,Fclub's Sandy Park ground on Thursday 7
OL,9,FMay to vote on an expression of
OL,10,Finterest to buy the club.
OL,12,FBusinessman Tony Rowe, the CEO and
OL,13,Fchairman of The Chiefs, has poured
OL,14,Fmillions of pounds of his own money
OL,15,Finto the club.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
