OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1778328667
OL,3,CExeter Chiefs could soon be under new
OL,4,CAmerican ownership
OL,6,FHe addressed the meeting to talk
OL,7,Fthrough a letter of intent from Cannae
OL,8,FHoldings Inc's (Black Knight Sports
OL,9,Fand Entertainment), which outlined
OL,10,Ftheir interest in purchasing all the
OL,11,Fshares of Exeter Rugby Club Group plc.
OL,13,FMembers voted by a majority to permit
OL,14,Fthe sale of the company.
OL,16,FAfterwards Mr Rowe said: "This does
OL,17,Fnot represent a firm offer. It is just
OL,18,Fa non-binding expression of interest
OL,19,Fat this stage but, hopefully, an offer
OL,20,Fwill follow and we can begin
OL,21,Fnegotiating the terms of the sale."
