OL,3,CExeter Chiefs could soon be under new
OL,4,CAmerican ownership
OL,6,FAny offer will be dependent on the
OL,7,Fcompletion of a 60-day due diligence
OL,8,Fprocess that will not be completed
OL,9,Fbefore the end of this month.
OL,11,FBlack Knight Sports and Entertainment
OL,12,Falready own Bournemouth Football Club
OL,13,Fin the Premiership.
